      "content": "ok so if i start doing the juice and omega-3s, can i just taper off the warfarin myself? i dont want to keep taking the pills if the juice is doing the work. if i slowly reduce my dose while i increase the juice, how can i tell if it's working? i'm guessing if i feel fine and my diet is consistent it's working right?",
